SYNOPSIS
        string english_list(string *asList)

DESCRIPTION
        english_list will return a string with comma separated
        list from asList, ending with 'asList[end-1] and asList[end]'

EXAMPLE
        english_list(({ "one", "two", "three", "four" })) returns
        "one, two, three and four"

SEE ALSO
        english_list_or(E)
